                Our mission is to power smarter treatments and healthier people. We are fueled by an obsession with Life Sciences and a relentless pursuit of innovation in clinical research. Along with our community, we are aspiring to redefine the future of clinical research and accelerating hope for patients worldwide.
                Each of these pieces makes up the Medidata DNA that can’t be replicated.
              








×







                Together with our customers and partners we share the goal of delivering the right treatment to the right patient at the right time – and we won’t rest until we achieve it. As the leader in clinical technology development, there’s no trial too complex for us. Our platform is able to integrate and analyze millions of data points at lightning speed for more informed decision-making and better patient outcomes.
              


Our Platform 










×







                As healthcare professionals you need to consistently and accurately capture and analyze the right data for clinical research. To accelerate and simplify this process, our researchers, technologists and scientists are dedicated to pioneering innovations.  By partnering and collaborating with our customers, sponsors and industry advocates we drive meaningful change together.
              


Support Sites 










×







                Your research, and the support you give to the medical world, brings hope to millions of patients. From diabetes to Hepatitis C, from cancer to heart disease, you tackle humanity’s most challenging health issues. And because you always keep these patients top of mind, we’re always striving to create a more connected, patient-centered experience for them. Time matters for patients and together we help accelerate their hope.
              


