Clinical Cloud
Study PlanningSite SupportPatient EngagementStudy ConductOptimize Outcomes 
















Clinical Cloud


The Medidata Clinical Cloud is a technological architecture dedicated to transforming clinical research for life science companies and the patients who depend on them. 
With a Platform that is intuitive, integrated and intelligent, we utilize our industry leading set of clinical data to optimize the outcomes of your research at every stage.






















Clinical Cloud
Study PlanningSite SupportPatient EngagementStudy ConductOptimize Outcomes 










 




The Platform for transforming clinical research
The life science industry is under pressure. As key patents are expiring, pharma and biotech companies are challenged to bring new and better treatments to patients.
One critical roadblock is that clinical trials—vital for proving safety and efficacy—are long, complicated and expensive.  The Medidata Clinical Cloud is a unique vertical SaaS platform solely dedicated to transforming clinical research for life science companies and the patients who depend on them.  
Because it's SaaS, the Clinical Cloud has been proven to scale from small biotechs conducting one study to major pharmas conducting dozens. Because it’s Medidata, the Clinical Cloud lets you:
Cut clinical development costs
Mitigate clinical development risks
Deliver drugs and devices to market faster
The Clinical Cloud already encompasses eight billion clinical records from more than three million patients across more than 12,000 studies. And more than one million data points are added daily. Find out why hundreds of sponsors and CROs are already in the Clinical Cloud, and how it can help you transform clinical development today.
 

 









        Plan Study      




Planning
The Medidata Planning Cloud slashes downstream cost, time and risk by building better execution right into your study design and budget.
Site Budgeting, Design Optimization, Site Negotiation




Payments
Payments Cloud is Medidata’s solution for integrating processing and disbursements to clinical sites across the globe.
Site Payment Calculation, Site Payment Disbursement, Financial Reporting and Transparency, Accruals and Forecasting









        Support Sites      




Monitoring
Use the industry’s leading cloud solution for monitoring clinical trial data to enhance data quality, improve CRA productivity and target monitoring resources where they’re needed most.
Centralized Monitoring & Analytics, Targeted SDV









        Engage Patients      




Patient Cloud
Patient Cloud captures data from apps and wearable sensors to accelerate patient­ centric clinical research.
ePro, AppConnect, SensorLink









        Conduct Study      




Data Capture
Use the world’s leading cloud solution for electronic data capture to enhance data quality, increase process efficiency and boost site satisfaction.
Electronic Data Capture, Medical Imaging, Clinical Data Management Systems




Study Management
Go beyond basic EDC and enrich your trials with best‐in‐class data management, randomization, medical coding, safety and more—all within an integrated platform.
Clinical Data Management, Safety Data Transmission, Trial Supply Management, Medical Coding, Randomization









        Optimize Outcomes      




Data & Analytics
Leverage our industry-leading dataset and analytics expertise to optimize your clinical trials.
Clinical Business Analytics, Cross-Platform Reporting, Operational Analytics, Trial Assurance, Statistical Analytics













  Get Started
Medidata’s services team and Services Partners can help get your trial up and running quickly.
Quickly gain know-how in the platform through Medidata Academy’s extensive courses and flexible training formats.

































