                Medidata Solutions, Inc. (MDSO): Product News News              








MDSO – Confirms will be first technology company ever selected by ASCO to present its scientific innovation to advance clinical research and further drug development.

May 17, 2017 | 6:04pm | By StockNews.com Staff 
 












 



Product News 





Key Facts Surrounding This News Item


MDSO had a POWR Rating of A (Strong Buy) coming into today.
MDSO was 2.19% above its 10-Day Moving Average coming into today.
MDSO was 5.56% above its 20-Day Moving Average coming into today.
MDSO was 14.40% above its 50-Day Moving Average coming into today.
MDSO was 23.47% above its 100-Day Moving Average coming into today.
MDSO was 27.71% above its 200-Day Moving Average coming into today.
MDSO had returned +41.63% year-to-date leading up to today’s news, versus a +7.87% return from the benchmark S&P 500 during the same period.

More Info About Medidata Solutions, Inc. (MDSO)

Medidata Solutions is a provider of cloud-based solutions for clinical research in life sciences, transforming clinical development through its advanced applications and intelligent data analytics. The company was founded in 1999 and is based in New York, New York. View our full MDSO ticker page with ratings, news, and more.
 






 


